Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170619%2F20058391&h=499407a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20170619/20058391</a><br />\n【專題籽】銀幣處理員日日數大餅 一蚊幾毫的專業"},{"pid":"11d160844ecce3974b27f99ef24a0b9c0f976896","tid":1039333,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"72969f8a0c0ae5e62bee20bc1bb08757619bc3b9","tid":1039333,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"bcca36ff0c8d91e2669f00ea355d9a67be47fe47","tid":1039333,"uid":27675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e6755f4fd8fc22c0e397b03032827e13cb308ee","tid":1039333,"uid":91833,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:18:38.000Z","msg":"蚊，毫"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T11:23:40.000Z","msg":"你搵本教「蚊」嘅出嚟睇比大家欣賞下囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:06:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20170619/20058391\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170619%2F20058391&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=ed15a948\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170619%2F20058391&h=499407a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20170619/20058391</a><br />\n【專題籽】銀幣處理員日日數大餅 一蚊幾毫的專業"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"「來到才知道，一蚊幾毫都可會累積成千元萬元。」說着，他就提起一袋已分類的硬幣入布袋，看起來像小包白米的2毫硬幣，「這已經是1,000元啦，都是錢。」經驗豐富的梁明，把錢袋擺一擺，就能憑聲音認銀，「這袋，聲音沉實的，是10元硬幣；這一袋，清脆爽朗的，一定是2元硬幣。」<br />\n這裏十多人，每天共處理（收回並包裝）超過100萬枚硬幣。以一袋2元硬幣為例，看起來，一小包，卻最少重8公斤。「初入行眼看硬幣細細袋，以為工作好輕鬆，但重複提着硬幣袋在工場來回，三兩次就好辛苦，手臂肌肉非常痠軟。不過，都習慣了。」每天梁明和同事，從早上起就在工場內團團轉，把一袋一袋的硬幣搬上搬落，分類包裝上貨架；到特定時間，梁明就會拍拍手向大家宣佈，「同事，我們現在先做體操。」原來體操時段是由梁明帶領拉筋伸展，才回去開工，「這是公司安排的運動時段。同事都害羞不肯帶領做運動，那就由我來領頭啦。」他一貫隨和的說。"},{"pid":"eadf6c5705a8e7230e8f83da60d1c5a405ec00d4","tid":1039333,"uid":28654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:08:59.000Z","msg":"元&amp;毫"},{"pid":"b6847fac36dfffb03111c2603f82ec9a6ef8802b","tid":1039333,"uid":2059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"屌你個正負評次序fake撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85de881881853829e9c72406c3254ff43ee740a","tid":1039333,"uid":226524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6847fac36dfffb03111c2603f82ec9a6ef8802b","tid":1039333,"uid":2059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"屌你個正負評次序fake撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都中咗伏"}]}